name: NAVE
description:
NAVE arcade is an artgentinean proyect. An arcade built by argentinean game developers Videogamo Inc.
A little ship that in the face of adversity becomes big, enormous. Its goal. TO RESIST.
Gif made out of frames from the 10 year aniversary event.
To be witness of such a magnificent endeavour, to watch its voyages has been a priviledge of mine.
Today that I travel through a different space, around old and new faces, I start a new journey and I join a different vessel.

Archain is the way!
